Item ID12538

The dragon full helm ornament kit is an ornament kit that can be obtained as a reward from elite Treasure Trails. It can be attached to the Dragon full helm, making it a Dragon full helm (g). Once attached, the ornamented helm cannot be sold, but the kit can be detached from the helm and sold.
